      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>道隱無名。夫唯道，善貸且成。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The Dao is hidden, and has no name; but it is the Dao which is skilful at imparting (to all things what they need) and making them complete.</seg>
